{"tid":2152841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"毛記葵涌 跌36% 現報0.99，萬華媒體昨日以平均價每股約1.547元減持2.5%股份","createTime":"2020-08-12T08:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T14:27:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ebcc26b6396af6727a8c9bd782be894dfa3a04b","tid":2152841,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543151-20200811.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543151-20200811.htm&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=e4a0513f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543151-20200811.htm&h=dd259115\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543151-20200811.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n萬華媒體公布，今日(11日) 以平均價每股約1.547元，出售共675萬股毛記葵涌股份，相當於毛記葵涌全部已發行股本約2.5%，出售所得款項約1040萬元。交易完成後，萬華媒體持有毛記葵涌權益由7.5%降至5%。<br />\n<br />\n萬華媒體表示，預計交易所得收益約710萬元。集團可藉今次出售變現部分在毛記葵涌的投資，提升集團現金狀況及營運資金。"},{"pid":"ddd8b33875f68e8931565845332ef4ae90eb3e21","tid":2152841,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:56:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">萬華媒體再減持0.56%毛記葵涌股份</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543361-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543361-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=191cce3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543361-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bf844da2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543361-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n萬華媒體進一步減持毛記葵涌股份，今日以<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">每股平均價約1.275元</span></span></strong>，出售150萬股毛記葵涌股份，相當於已發行股本約0.56%，套現共190萬元。交易完成後，萬華媒體在毛記葵涌的持股由5%降低至4.44%。<br />\n<br />\n萬華媒體預計，今次出售將錄得收益約120萬元。"},{"pid":"91ef51f93f783b59f0b7b1dd119a398e5bd2c038","tid":2152841,"uid":218166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"莊家逆市執到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c0f397fd2bda9236092f4bc72423bfccd825b5","tid":2152841,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91ef51f93f783b59f0b7b1dd119a398e5bd2c038","tid":2152841,"uid":218166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"莊家逆市執到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:07:12.000Z","msg":"支持黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86bbaa5ad9f507ff6455720fcec8740cbd81197","tid":2152841,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"1040萬. 一個3房單位都難"},{"pid":"2660c36615a35ae337b5b371277b6959610e6d91","tid":2152841,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91ef51f93f783b59f0b7b1dd119a398e5bd2c038","tid":2152841,"uid":218166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"莊家逆市執到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"兒登仔炒高比中資出貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbce8f1435e96a9997b38b3ca2954f8464d55cff","tid":2152841,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b86bbaa5ad9f507ff6455720fcec8740cbd81197","tid":2152841,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re